# Quiz: What do you already know about food and diabetes?
If you've recently been diagnosed with either Type 1, Type 2 or another type
of diabetes, what do you know about how food affects the condition? There are
lots of myths about food and diabetes. Can you have fruit? Is it OK to drink
Have a go at our quiz... you might be in for a surprise or two.
